# Regex recap

ab
a|b     a or b
a+      one or more a
a*      zero or more a
a?      zero or one times a
[abc] [a-z]
[a-z]*
a{2,5}  aa,aaa,aaaa,aaaaa
[^a]    anything but a
.       joker, length 1 (not EOL)
...     length 3

a|b*    * has higher prio:  a, empty, b, bb, bbb ...
(a|b)*  {a,b}^*

regex101.com
